{
  "stem": "19550.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then build the airplane fuselages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this was the model, so to say, for the three other work camps that I was at, except for Dachau.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It really was four camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And except for Allach, it was all on the ground in mines.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Originally in France, it was in ore mines, and Heilbronn and [INAUDIBLE] it was in salt mines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I was-- as the airlines moved westward, or eastward for them, we were-- kept being evacuated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I went from [INAUDIBLE] to either Heilbronn or Kochendorf or vice versa.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I don't know exactly which came first.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then from there, I went to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And from Dachau, I went to Allach.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And in Allach, we were working at the BMW factory, still supposedly building-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] building airplane fuselages.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I think I can confidently say that we, in the one year that I was shuttled from one camp to another, I-- I don't think that one fully completed piece of airplane fuselage ever left our factory.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "May have been half fabricated, but in most cases, obviously, we didn't know what the heck we were doing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And a lot of time was spent with [INAUDIBLE] it on our part or on the part of whatever forced laborers who were in the area, and who were enrolled in the same enterprise.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then from Allach, we were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] put in-- actually, at times, I had worked in other places, like in the airport at Munich, and the railroads at Munich that were bombed out by the Allies.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And most of the times, I was called on to be a translator.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when we were sent out from Allach, we were shuttled, I would say, not more than about 30 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
